{"tid":766463,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)安娜貝爾1-2 詭屋驚凶實錄1-2","createTime":"2018-08-03T15:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T20:23:17.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51e5bd6b67e511ad822783663090aa145bda4285","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e2690973\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=745644ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=196d5f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/da/Annabelle_Creation_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fda%2FAnnabelle_Creation_Poster.jpg&h=eae72161&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://philippines.liketimes.me/file/parts/Ia30d9db/b1da0701a5400aea863739642208f3c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphilippines.liketimes.me%2Ffile%2Fparts%2FIa30d9db%2Fb1da0701a5400aea863739642208f3c4.jpg&h=e59a3e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1f/Conjuring_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1f%2FConjuring_poster.jpg&h=e4680cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg&h=7175e393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.手藝精巧的洋娃娃製作師山謬及其妻子遭逢愛女小貝的死亡意外，思女心切的他們終日祈禱能夠重見愛女，而他們的祈求竟獲得回應：「小貝」表達希望能夠附身在娃娃身上的願望。但是很快地，這對夫妻發現附身在娃娃身上的不是他們的女兒，於是決定用聖經將「它」關起來。十二年後，這對夫妻款待了一名修女及幾名孤兒院的女孩們來到他們家，但這群女孩很快地成為安娜貝爾娃娃的新目標<br />\n<br />\n2.内容大概是說 1970s時， 有2個護士 Lou &amp; Donna， 其中Donna有個娃娃就是那個annebelle dolls， 那是Donna 在小時候她媽媽送她的生日禮物。<br />\n在她們搬進那間公寓後， 她們發現那個娃娃會在她們不在時移動， 有一次在她們回來後， 她們發現那個娃娃跪在門前的椅子上面對著她們， 她們之後試著讓娃娃以同樣的姿勢跪著， 發現娃娃根本不能跪著， 只會一直往前倒下。<br />\n<br />\n3.1971年，美國羅德島州哈維爾，佩倫一家七口搬進了一棟郊區大宅，一家之主羅傑與妻子卡洛琳、和五個女兒&mdash;安卓莉亞、南希、克莉絲汀、辛蒂與愛普原本對新房子充滿期待，但不到幾天就覺得這棟新房子越來越不對勁；寵物狗在搬進去的第二天就神秘死去、所有的鐘全部停在淩晨三點零七分、房子每當夜裏都會飄來一股腐爛屍臭、所有的門在夜裏會頻繁開了又關、卡洛琳的身上頻繁會出現不該存在的淤青、克莉絲汀睡覺時老是覺得有人在抓她的腳、有夢遊症的辛蒂睡著時會用頭不停地撞擊一個老櫥櫃、而愛普在寵物狗死後不停地在跟一個叫羅伊的小孩說話..<br />\n<br />\n4.1976年，超自然現象探究者艾德與蘿琳&middot;華倫夫婦辦理了「阿米蒂維爾凶宅事件」，協助堪稱屋子裏發生了多起靈異事件的盧茲一家，來確認該屋子是否在兩年前發生了一場慘烈的血洗事件：一個名叫小羅納德&middot;迪菲歐殘忍在屋子裏殺光了他的家人後，在法庭上稱自己遭魔鬼附身而被迫殺死家人，最後沒被法官採信而被判處連續六個終身監禁。蘿琳運用自己與生俱來的陰陽眼來探查屋子各處時<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=07b8447f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b1813ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbc3f96708fece901ff3dabac01a32c102dd881","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24788a46ad9b35dc95f3a1e4f4cacd8e07d32d2f","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252273b6c54354e56c80929b3942ddb6e1191a3d","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f106edc2d9bc918bbb3a17a8e6515af80aae80df","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dcafc6c32368ffb0941d1a89142c37bb60b064","tid":766463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgm